{
  "id": "6a082ab07a71822d15746660",
  "title": "井戸端の心理的安全性",
  "created": 1778920141,
  "updated": 1778921251,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a082ab07a71822d15746660",
      "text": "井戸端の心理的安全性",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778920141,
      "updated": 1778920141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a082b490000000000aad3b6",
      "text": "[アホな質問をたくさんするぞ〜]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778920266,
      "updated": 1778920267
    },
    {
      "id": "6a082ad50000000000aad3b3",
      "text": " [無知をひけらかすこと]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778920150,
      "updated": 1778920340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a082b880000000000b626cf",
      "text": " [くだらないことや未完成の内容を書いて敷居を下げ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778920329,
      "updated": 1778920379
    },
    {
      "id": "6a082bec0000000000f9b151",
      "text": "[知識をひけらかすこと]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778920429,
      "updated": 1778920434
    },
    {
      "id": "6a082bf20000000000f9b152",
      "text": " [知識は積極的にひけらかす]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778920434,
      "updated": 1778920492
    },
    {
      "id": "6a082dc00000000000203878",
      "text": " [「知識をひけらかすことは善である」という価値観]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778920897,
      "updated": 1778920898
    },
    {
      "id": "6a082c2c0000000000f9b153",
      "text": " [問わず語りをしよう]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778920493,
      "updated": 1778920531
    },
    {
      "id": "6a082afd0000000000aad3b4",
      "text": "[井戸端の何を書いても大丈夫はもう古いのでは？]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778920189,
      "updated": 1778920429
    },
    {
      "id": "6a082b030000000000aad3b5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778920196,
      "updated": 1778920196
    },
    {
      "id": "6a082acc0000000000aad3b1",
      "text": "[心理的安全性]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778920141,
      "updated": 1778920147
    },
    {
      "id": "6a082f1d0000000000203879",
      "text": " [心理的安全性を高める]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778921245,
      "updated": 1778921251
    },
    {
      "id": "6a082acd0000000000aad3b2",
